WEBVTT

00:09:59.000 --> 00:10:01.226
kindness, patience --

00:10:01.250 --> 00:10:03.667
we can practice these things every day.

00:10:04.875 --> 00:10:07.601
And while practice
will definitely make you better,

00:10:07.625 --> 00:10:11.393
I have to promise you
it's also not going to make you perfect.

00:10:11.417 --> 00:10:12.768
I do this for a living

00:10:12.792 --> 00:10:15.601
and every day I think and talk
about healthy relationships,

00:10:15.625 --> 00:10:18.226
and still I do unhealthy things.

00:10:18.250 --> 00:10:21.643
Just the other day as I was trying
to shuttle my four kids out the door

00:10:21.667 --> 00:10:24.643
amidst quarreling, squabbling
and complaints about breakfast,

00:10:24.667 --> 00:10:26.768
I completely lost it.

00:10:26.792 --> 00:10:28.934
With an intentionally angry edge,

00:10:28.958 --> 00:10:30.268
I screamed,